Subject: [PATCH 0221/2241] ARM: mvebu: a395-gp: add support for the Armada 395
 GP Board

This commit adds description for the following features for this board:

- Serial port
- PCIe interfaces
- USB2.0
- USB3.0
- SDIO
- 1024 MiB NAND-FLASH
- SATA
- I2C buses
- SPI bus

